{"aid": "ilhow8ogv503d5", "result": {"folders": ["课堂问答"], "unique_views": 76, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"data": "ilg9cvihxi82vw", "anon": "full", "when": "2016-03-06T07:49:18Z", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "ilgbggr2ta9er", "when": "2016-03-06T08:48:05Z", "to": "ilg9cvicbk32vv", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "ilg9cvicbk32vv", "bookmarked": 5, "no_answer": 0, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2016-03-06T08:48:05Z", "config": {}, "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_order": 2, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "id": "ilgbggqyjtdeq", "history": [{"content": "<p>这是一个好问题。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>每个算法都是同时有优点和缺点的。通常的做法是&#xff0c;只把算法用在它适合的场合。buddy算法比较适合于大小变化比较大的小块物理内存管理。在极端情况&#xff0c;如果要分配的块大小都是260字节左右&#xff0c;它会有一半左右的存储空间的浪费。这就不好了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>有兴趣的同学&#xff0c;可以查一下&#xff0c;并在本帖后面回复你对下面问题的观点。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>在真实系统中&#xff0c;buddy算法都用在什么地方&#xff1f;这些地方有什么特征&#xff1f;还有其他实际使用的物理内存分配算法吗&#xff1f;它们的特征是什么样的&#xff1f;</p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-03-06T08:48:05Z"}]}], "no_answer_followup": 0, "nr": 656, "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "status": "active", "tags": ["student", "课堂问答"], "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2016-03-06T07:49:18Z", "is_tag_good": false, "type": "question", "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1457337122800, "tag_good": [{"name": "Yong XIANG", "admin": true, "photo": null, "us": false, "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie"}], "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie"], "history": [{"content": "<p>看完视频&#xff0c;我对Buddy内存分配算法有一些疑问&#xff0c;首先就是感觉这个算法似乎会浪费挺多的内存&#xff0c;比如说申请768M&#xff0c;那就要给出1G&#xff0c;这可一下子浪费了256M啊= =&#xff0c;而且感觉虽然这个算法分配是非常巧妙和快速的&#xff0c;可是万一内存空间不够的时候整理起来好像也很麻烦呀&#xff08;为了保持那个2^n对齐&#xff0c;显然不能简单地把已经分配的块压缩起来&#xff09;&#xff0c;是这些问题我没有考虑清楚还是说实际工程中的Buddy算法还有更多的改进&#xff1f;</p>", "anon": "full", "subject": "为什么我感觉Buddy分配算法似乎会浪费更多内存&#xff0c;而且难以进行整理啊", "created": "2016-03-06T07:49:18Z"}]}, "error": null}